        {"item": "Lettuce leaves (bibb or iceberg)", "quantity": "12"}
      ],
      "steps": [
        "Combine hoisin, soy sauce, rice vinegar, sesame oil, ginger, and garlic in a small bowl. Set aside.",
        "Heat cooking oil in large skillet over medium heat. Add ground chicken, crumble and cook until browned.",
